body:
Fixes #6051.

This makes Spack builds on OS X faithful to `compilers.yaml` unless they have to be different (e.g. for XCode builds).  Now *only* packages that set `use_xcode=True` will use the XCode compiler wrappers for clang.

@balay: can you see if this fixes your issue?

@mathstuf @davydden 

Ping @alalazo b/c this adds a `force=True` option to `EnvironmentModifications`, in cases where you know you're overwriting an already-set value.
